What is EC2?

EC2 stands for Elastic Compute Cloud.

It is a virtual server in AWS.

Simple Definition

EC2 is a virtual computer (server) that AWS provides over the internet.

Instead of buying a physical server, AWS gives you a virtual server that you can use whenever you need.

